<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3999895>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Bathytropa rifensis sp. nov. from St. 15, paratype ♀: (A) adult specimen, dorsal view; (B) dorsal scale-seta; (C) scale-seta on posterior margins of segments; (D) cephalon, dorsal view; (E) cephalon, frontal view; (F) pleonite 5, telson and right uropod; (G) antennule; (H) antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3999895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3999897>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Bathytropa rifensis sp. nov. from St. 15, paratype ♂: (A) left mandible; (B) right mandible; (C) maxillule; (D) maxilla; (E) maxilliped; (F) pereopod 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3999897/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3999899>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Bathytropa rifensis sp. nov. from St. 8, paratype ♂: (A) pereopod 7; (B) genital papilla and pleopod 1; (C) pleopod 2; (D) pleopod 3 exopod; (E) pleopod 4 exopod; (F) pleopod 5 exopod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3999899/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

